&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At Poka, we’re transforming how frontline teams operate, learn, and solve problems.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our connected worker platform is purpose-built for manufacturing, empowering frontline workers to share knowledge, collaborate in real-time, and drive continuous improvement. Think of it as the missing digital link, bringing the human interface into the stack of the Smart Factory, generating the right data and insights that drive entirely new scales of process improvements.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We’re proud to support global leaders like Nestlé, Bosch, Mars, and Danone in their digital transformation journeys and as part of the IFS family, our reach and impact continue to grow globally.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;691&quot; data-end=&quot;840&quot;&gt;If you thrive on building relationships, opening doors, and helping manufacturers modernize the way their frontline teams work, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;842&quot; data-end=&quot;1221&quot;&gt;We’re looking for an Enterprise Account Executive to join our growing Sales team and help bring Poka’s connected worker platform to manufacturers around the world. You’ll work with some of the industry’s most recognized brands, helping them tackle operational challenges, accelerate digital transformation, and unlock measurable business impact across their frontline operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1223&quot; data-end=&quot;1388&quot;&gt;This is a high-impact role for someone who combines strong commercial instincts with a genuine understanding of manufacturing environments and enterprise SaaS sales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;dhw6ft&quot; data-start=&quot;1390&quot; data-end=&quot;1413&quot;&gt;What you’ll be doing&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1415&quot; data-end=&quot;2406&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ad8caa&quot; data-start=&quot;1415&quot; data-end=&quot;1562&quot;&gt;Identify and develop new business opportunities through market research, outbound prospecting, and collaboration with the Sales Development team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;3rg715&quot; data-start=&quot;1563&quot; data-end=&quot;1702&quot;&gt;Own the full sales cycle, from discovery and needs analysis through product demonstrations, proposal development, negotiation, and close.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1rwjogj&quot; data-start=&quot;1703&quot; data-end=&quot;1839&quot;&gt;Build strong business cases tailored to each prospect’s operational priorities, demonstrating the value and impact of Poka’s platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1td0z9p&quot; data-start=&quot;1840&quot; data-end=&quot;1977&quot;&gt;Partner closely with Customer Success and cross-functional teams to ensure a seamless customer journey and long-term value realization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;gz1jw3&quot; data-start=&quot;1978&quot; data-end=&quot;2072&quot;&gt;Maintain accurate opportunity tracking, forecasting, and account activity within Salesforce.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;iw4eq3&quot; data-start=&quot;2073&quot; data-end=&quot;2193&quot;&gt;Share customer insights and market feedback with leadership to help shape go-to-market strategy and product direction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;164m0gt&quot; data-start=&quot;2194&quot; data-end=&quot;2305&quot;&gt;Contribute to lead generation initiatives and campaigns by leveraging customer knowledge and industry trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;k86h8j&quot; data-start=&quot;2306&quot; data-end=&quot;2406&quot;&gt;Represent Poka at trade shows, industry events, networking opportunities, and virtual conferences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;bhay4c&quot; data-start=&quot;2408&quot; data-end=&quot;2425&quot;&gt;What you bring

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At Poka, we’re transforming how frontline teams operate, learn, and solve problems.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
